Package com.techhounds.houndutil.houndauto

Class AutoManager

java.lang.Object
com.techhounds.houndutil.houndauto.AutoManager
public class AutoManager extends Object
Handles scheduling of autos and display of paths to NetworkTables. Uses the /HoundLog/autonomous table.

Use init() in robotInit, periodicUpdate() in disabledPeriodic, runSelectedRoutine() in autonomousInit, and endRoutine() in autonomousExit.
